      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle retains its original showroom luster, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior. Mechanically beyond reproach, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. A rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
